                               <div class=\"menuSectionItem_title\">会社概要</div>\n                            </a>\n                        </div>\n                        <!-- /.menuSectionItem -->\n\n                        <ul class=\"menuSectionList\">\n                            <li><a href=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/about/history/\">沿革</a></li>\n                        </ul>\n                        <!-- /.menuSectionList -->\n\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"menuContainer_item menuContainer_item-02\">\n\n                        <div class=\"menuSectionItem\">\n                            <a href=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/business/\">\n                                <div class=\"menuSectionItem_title\">事業案内</div>\n                            </a>\n                        </div>\n                        <!-- /.menuSectionItem -->\n\n                        <ul class=\"menuSectionList\">\n                            <li><a href=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/business/lumber/\">木材物流</a></li>\n                            <li><a href=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/business/container/\">コンテナ物流</a></li>\n                            <li><a href=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/business/automobile/\">車輌物流</a></li>\n                            <li><a href=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/business/general/\">その他物流</a></li>\n                        </ul>\n                        <!-- /.menuSectionList -->\n\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"menuContainer_item menuContainer_item-03\">\n                    <div class=\"menuSectionItem\">\n                        <a href=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/recruit/\">\n                            <div class=\"menuSectionItem_title\">採用情報</div>\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                    <!-- /.menuSectionItem -->\n                    <div class=\"menuSectionItem\">\n                        <a href=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/sdgs/\">\n                            <div class=\"menuSectionItem_title\">SDGsの取組</div>\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                    <!-- /.menuSectionItem -->\n\n                    <div class=\"menuSectionItem\">\n                        <a href=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/contact/\">\n                            <div class=\"menuSectionItem_title\">お問い合せ</div>\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                    <!-- /.menuSectionItem -->\n\n                    <div class=\"menuSectionItem\">\n                        <a href=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/sitemap/\">\n                            <div class=\"menuSectionItem_title\">サイトマップ</div>\n                        </a>\n                    </div>\n                    <!-- /.menuSectionItem -->\n\n                </div>\n\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <!-- /.menuContainer -->\n\n<div class=\"commonTitle\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h1 class=\"commonTitle_title commonTitle_title-03\"><img src=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/wp-content/themes/niyaku-theme/cmn/img/recruit/pic_titlte.png?v=202601260546\" alt=\"\"></h1>\n        <div class=\"commonTitle_info\">採用情報</div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<!-- /.commonTitle -->\n\n<div class=\"pnkz\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <ul class=\"pnkz_list\">\n            <li><a href=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/\">トップ</a></li>\n            <li class=\"active\">採用情報</li>\n        </ul>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<!-- /.pnkz -->\n\n\n<div class=\"eyeCatch\" style=\"background-image: url(https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/wp-content/themes/niyaku-theme/cmn/img/recruit/pic_eyecatch.jpg?v=202601260546)\">\n    <div class=\"eyeCatch_inner\">あなたの強い想いが<br>物流の新しい未来を<span class=\"spBr\"></span>切り開きます。</div>\n    <div class=\"eyeCatch_sp\"><img src=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/wp-content/themes/niyaku-theme/cmn/img/recruit/pic_eyecatch_sp.jpg?v=202601260546\" alt=\"\"></div>\n</div>\n<!-- /.eyeCatch -->\n\n<div class=\"recruitContainer\">\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"recruitContainer_text\">港湾運送事業は、国際輸送に欠かせない存在だからこそ、日常生活に直結し、安定感や将来性も抜群です。<br>\n            また、ありふれた業種ではないため、当社で活躍する社員のほとんどが未経験からスタートしています。<br>\n            重要なのは、未経験者でも仕事に取り組む姿勢です。</div>\n\n        <div class=\"recruitIndexPeople\">\n\n            <h2 class=\"recruitIndexPeople_title\">先輩の声</h2>\n\n            <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain\">\n\n                <a href=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/recruit/rec01/\" class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_item\" style=\"padding-bottom:0;\">\n                    <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_pic\"><img src=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/wp-content/themes/niyaku-theme/cmn/img/recruit/pic_staff_01.jpg?v=202601260546\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_name\">営業部</div>\n                    <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_info\" style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">管理職</div>\n                </a>\n\n                <a href=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/recruit/rec02/\" class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_item\" style=\"padding-bottom:0;\">\n                    <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_pic\"><img src=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/wp-content/themes/niyaku-theme/cmn/img/recruit/pic_staff_02.jpg?v=202601260546\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_name\">廿日市営業所</div>\n                    <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_info\" style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">所属</div>\n                </a>\n\n                <a href=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/recruit/rec03/\" class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_item\" style=\"padding-bottom:0;\">\n                    <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_pic\"><img src=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/wp-content/themes/niyaku-theme/cmn/img/recruit/pic_staff_03.jpg?v=202601260546\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_name\">営業部 営業グループ</div>\n                    <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_info\" style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">所属</div>\n\n                </a>\n\n                <a href=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/recruit/rec04/\" class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_item\" style=\"padding-bottom:0;\">\n                    <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_pic\"><img src=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/wp-content/themes/niyaku-theme/cmn/img/recruit/pic_staff_04.jpg?v=202601260546\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_name\">通関部</div>\n                    <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_info\" style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">所属</div>\n\n                </a>\n\n                <a href=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/recruit/rec05/\" class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_item\" style=\"padding-bottom:0;\">\n                    <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_pic\"><img src=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/wp-content/themes/niyaku-theme/cmn/img/recruit/pic_staff_05.jpg?v=202601260546\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_name\">営業部 自動車チーム</div>\n                    <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_info\" style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">所属</div>\n                </a>\n\n                <a href=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/recruit/rec06/\" class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_item\" style=\"padding-bottom:0;\">\n                    <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_pic\"><img src=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/wp-content/themes/niyaku-theme/cmn/img/recruit/pic_staff_06.jpg?v=202601260546\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_name\">港運部</div>\n                    <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_info\" style=\"margin-bottom:5px;\">管理職</div>\n                </a>\n\n                <a href=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/recruit/rec07/\" class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_item\" style=\"padding-bottom:0;\">\n                    <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_pic\"><img src=\"https://hi-niyaku.co.jp/wp-content/themes/niyaku-theme/cmn/img/recruit/pic_staff_07.jpg?v=202601260546\" alt=\"\"></div>\n                    <div class=\"recruitIndexPeopleMain_name\">港運部 専門・技能職チ